space.world

Class BeamShooter

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.world.Entity
      • space.world.NonStationary
        • space.world.BeamShooter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ViewableNonStationary, ViewableObject

    public class BeamShooter
extends NonStationary
    Represents an item which shoots beams. It constantly rotates until it is stopped. Once stopped, it fires beams.
